<div1 type="summary">
<p>Bill for hire of Negro.</p>
</div1>

<div1 type="body">


<p><person_mentioned>Moses Austin</person_mentioned> Dr
To <person_mentioned>Francis Major</person_mentioned></p>

<p>For the hire of <person_mentioned>Toney </person_mentioned>from the <date_mentioned n="01-14-1811">14 of Jany 1811</date_mentioned>
To the 16th of March following at $18,00 per Month</p>

<p>is_______________________________________	 $37. 50

<date_mentioned n="04-02-1811">2nd April</date_mentioned> 1 Days Work____________________    0. 75
							 _______
							 $38. 25
							 _______
<person_mentioned>Mr. Austin</person_mentioned> dtr___________________________  $36. 00

Crdt_____________________________________   $3. 62 1/2

Balance Due______________________________  $32. 37 1/2</p>

<p><location_mentioned>Mine a Burton</location_mentioned>
	<date_mentioned n="04-24-1811">April 24 1811</date_mentioned>   Recd. <person_mentioned>M Austin</person_mentioned> Note for the above <person_mentioned>Negro </person_mentioned>Hire
which when paid is in full of all accounts                   <person_mentioned>Fras. Major</person_mentioned></p>

